594
00:27:50.520 --> 00:27:52.880
I didn't push it out!
I was talking to you!

595
00:27:53.080 --> 00:27:54.960
-You did that on purpose.
-I did not do...

596
00:27:55.120 --> 00:27:55.960
-[Jeremy] Why?
-You did.

597
00:27:56.160 --> 00:27:59.520
