-[Kaleb] You were pushing the boom out.

598
00:28:01.920 --> 00:28:03.640
-[Kaleb] Fuck's sake.
-Stress.

599
00:28:04.320 --> 00:28:06.080
[Kaleb] Fuck me. It's like talking
