The pump and the glass. innit?

954
00:44:56.480 --> 00:44:58.880
[Lisa] Oh. it's filling up! Ah!

955
00:45:00.440 --> 00:45:01.560
Oh. what's it becoming?

956
00:45:05.120 --> 00:45:07.280
