-[Jeremy] It's Gerald!

957
00:45:07.480 --> 00:45:08.960
[cheering and laughing]

958
00:45:09.640 --> 00:45:11.920
-Look at that!
-[Lisa] Wow!

959
00:45:12.120 --> 00:45:14.200
That's your Christmas card sorted!

960
00:45:16.480 --> 00:45:20.000
