<i>to make fun of the government.</i>

977
00:46:06.280 --> 00:46:08.240
[soft music continues]

978
00:46:13.280 --> 00:46:15.600
<i>But all of us knew that to try and stop</i>

979
00:46:15.800 --> 00:46:19.160
