Hold the far gate!

989
00:46:53.440 --> 00:46:54.400
-[electrical shock]
-Fuck!

990
00:46:54.600 --> 00:46:55.760
Ah!

991
00:46:55.960 --> 00:46:57.000
We need a Christmas grotto.

